<blockquote>Some other facilities:</blockquote>

<ul>
<ul>
<li>
Deadline Dates uses information that users provide to help them stay on
track. Task calendars can be used to create a schedule that factors in
resource challenges such as scheduling conflicts or equipment downtime.<br>
<BR></li>

<li>
First time users can learn as they work on sample tutorial files.<br>
<BR></li>

<li>
The Project Map. This basic goal orientation covers the typical phases
in a project management cycle.<br>
<BR></li>

<li>
The Office Assistant. Though irritating sometimes, users can get answers
to their questions anytime.</li>
</ul>
</ul>

<center><img SRC="Image7.gif" height=79 width=87></center>

